Bluetooth Plugin for Exaile:

To make this plugin work:
1) Create a folder in your exaile plugin directory called "bluetooth_plugin" (or anything you wish)
2) Copy these three files to that directory

  a)__init__.py
  b)btSvr.py
  c)PLUGININFO
3) Restart exaile if it is running
4) Go to Edit>Preferences>Plugins and look around for "Bluetooth Controller"
5) Experiment!